item.title: Sponsor Packages
item.description: Dear Potential Sponsor: CyberTractor Challenge appreciates your interest in sponsoring our 3rd Annual event being held June 10-14, 2024, just 45 minutes north of the capitol of Iowa at the home of the Iowa State University Cyclones. As you read this, trainers are being approached by the Board of Directors to set classes, venue arrangements are being made, infrastructure is being created, recruiting of student applicants is underway, and more is in progress to bring this exciting event to life.
